Help me!

00:18.686 --> 00:22.022
BARCELONA, SPAIN.

00:29.196 --> 00:32.783
Jump! Please help me!

00:35.536 --> 00:36.579
Jump!

00:58.350 --> 00:59.852
Help me!

01:55.282 --> 01:57.284
MARADONA:
BLESSED DREAM

01:57.368 --> 01:58.911
SOUTH AMERICAN

02:04.667 --> 02:08.420
Finally, after many months
of negotiations,

02:09.004 --> 02:14.301
today, the man of the hour
will be joining FC Barcelona,

02:14.385 --> 02:15.719
Diego Armando Maradona.

02:15.803 --> 02:18.430
<i>Diego Armando Maradona</i>
<i>signed with FC Barcelona</i>

02:18.514 --> 02:22.434
<i>and arrived to a crowd waiting for him</i>
<i>at El Prat Airport this week.</i>

02:30.025 --> 02:32.152
Is it hard to win the Libertadores?

02:32.236 --> 02:34.738
- How are you, sir?
- Fine. How was your trip?

02:34.822 --> 02:37.616
<i>Diego Armando Maradona is a show.</i>

02:37.700 --> 02:41.829
<i>More than 40 journalists came</i>
<i>from Buenos Aires, Argentina.</i>

02:41.912 --> 02:44.874
<i>Photographers didn't leave him alone</i>
<i>for a second.</i>

02:45.875 --> 02:47.960
What's it like to be in Spain?

02:48.043 --> 02:49.962
I've only seen the airport.

02:50.963 --> 02:52.840
<i>All airports look the same.</i>

02:52.923 --> 02:57.469
Well, Diego, you can see the madness
your arrival has triggered,

02:57.553 --> 02:59.054
what you've stirred up.

02:59.138 --> 03:03.767
All these people expect you to repay
the money we've paid for you with titles.

03:03.851 --> 03:05.853
- You're putting pressure on me.
- Well.

03:06.770 --> 03:08.689
No, no, forget about them.

03:08.814 --> 03:11.901
No, we've set up
a press conference at the club.

03:11.984 --> 03:15.279
Diego, you came to a team
going through a losing streak,

03:15.362 --> 03:18.699
that hasn't won a major title in years,
is that extra pressure?

03:18.782 --> 03:22.494
What? Nuñez told me this was
the most successful team in Europe.

03:22.578 --> 03:24.914
Jorge, get a plane, let's go back to Boca.

03:24.997 --> 03:26.749
- Who is this?
- Is Gonzalo.

03:27.499 --> 03:29.126
A cameraman we brought with us.

03:29.209 --> 03:31.462
We're filming Maradona's documentary.

03:31.545 --> 03:34.381
Okay, Jorge, no, this is not Argentina.

03:34.465 --> 03:36.508
Barcelona isn't Boca.

03:36.592 --> 03:38.886
You can't do whatever you want here.

03:38.969 --> 03:41.180
There are procedures to follow.

03:41.263 --> 03:44.892
For example, statements for the media
can't be improvised.

03:44.975 --> 03:49.647
There's a press office
that decides where and when.

03:49.980 --> 03:52.191
So, if we want to get along,

03:52.274 --> 03:54.526
we should start off on the right foot.

03:54.610 --> 03:58.030
Asking that of Diego Maradona
would be contradictory.

03:58.113 --> 04:00.282
Better to start with the left.

04:00.741 --> 04:03.494
There was a lot of expectation
for the World Cup,

04:03.577 --> 04:05.955
but Argentina went out unceremoniously.

04:06.038 --> 04:08.540
Are you afraid that might happen
here?

04:08.624 --> 04:10.250
You had to be Argentinian.

04:10.542 --> 04:11.502
Of course.

04:11.669 --> 04:15.381
In my country,
journalists did a lot of damage.

04:15.464 --> 04:17.341
They said we were winning the war,

04:17.424 --> 04:19.510
while in the Falklands, kids were dying.

04:19.593 --> 04:21.428
I'm done with the Argentinian press.

04:21.512 --> 04:24.014
- No more questions.
- About the Falklands...

04:26.350 --> 04:29.228
- Is this the house you rented for us?
- Yes.

04:29.311 --> 04:31.271
- What do you think?
- I love it.

04:35.901 --> 04:37.569
- What, Morsa?
- Wait.

04:37.653 --> 04:41.490
Let me see this. I can't believe
the place you've got here.

04:41.573 --> 04:44.743
Mari, ask Kitty for the camera!

04:44.827 --> 04:47.871
Mari, give Kitty the camera
so she can take a picture!

04:47.955 --> 04:51.333
Wait, the van's waiting for you
to leave with the club.

04:51.417 --> 04:53.627
Come, take a picture for my folks.

04:53.711 --> 04:57.506
- These South Americans are so uncivilized.
- Yes.

04:57.589 --> 04:59.341
Mariano, honk the horn.

05:00.718 --> 05:02.636
Yes! Yes!

05:02.761 --> 05:03.804
Let's go!

05:04.972 --> 05:08.892
Remember when I told you
I thought Nuñez was an asshole?

05:08.976 --> 05:10.519
- Yes.
- It's now confirmed.

05:53.896 --> 05:57.691
Columbus conquered America,
but we'll conquer Europe, my friend.

05:57.775 --> 05:59.526
You know where I come from.

06:01.612 --> 06:04.531
Do you know how many times I hurt my foot

06:05.449 --> 06:07.326
from playing barefoot?

06:07.409 --> 06:09.495
You're here because you deserve it.

06:11.080 --> 06:13.499
- It's a miracle.
- No, it's not a miracle.

06:15.125 --> 06:17.586
It's a reward
for your effort and talent.

06:18.504 --> 06:19.630
It's thanks to you.

06:27.429 --> 06:29.473
Don't get mushy, they're watching us.

06:29.556 --> 06:31.141
I don't give a shit.

06:31.225 --> 06:32.351
All right, gentlemen,

06:32.434 --> 06:35.896
let's get going, the coach is waiting
in the locker room.

06:37.815 --> 06:39.066
Your teammates.

06:39.483 --> 06:42.277
- Urruti, the goalkeeper.
- Nice to meet you.

06:42.361 --> 06:43.695
- Welcome, Diego.
- Thanks.

06:43.779 --> 06:46.073
- José Manuel Martínez Toral.
- Pleasure.

06:46.156 --> 06:46.990
Likewise.

06:47.074 --> 06:50.077
And this is the other foreigner
on the team, Bernd Schuster.

06:50.160 --> 06:51.912
The German Nibelung.

06:51.995 --> 06:54.373
- What's up, Bernie?
- I'm great, Diego.

06:54.456 --> 06:56.959
What does he eat?
Steel? Look at his size.

06:57.918 --> 06:59.378
- Gerardo.
- Pleasure.

06:59.461 --> 07:00.963
Sánchez, the captain.

07:01.046 --> 07:01.880
- Hi.
- Hello.

07:01.964 --> 07:04.049
And this is our great strategist,

07:04.133 --> 07:06.009
he's German like Bernd.

07:06.093 --> 07:07.970
The coach, Udo Lattek.

07:08.053 --> 07:09.972
Udo Lattek. Nice to meet you.

07:10.472 --> 07:11.849
- Pleasure.
- Let me.

07:12.558 --> 07:15.727
It's a pleasure, Diego...

07:15.811 --> 07:17.437
To have... What was it?

07:17.521 --> 07:19.106
- To have.
- You do it.

07:19.189 --> 07:21.024
It's a pleasure to have you here.

07:23.318 --> 07:25.195
I hope we will get along well.

07:25.654 --> 07:28.198
We will, as long
as the translator is here.

07:36.498 --> 07:38.625
If you're a pro and you work hard,

07:38.709 --> 07:41.128
you'll have no problems
adapting to my team.

07:41.211 --> 07:42.629
That won't be a problem.

07:43.589 --> 07:44.798
I have a question.

07:45.549 --> 07:49.386
Who shouts out instructions during a game,
you or the translator?

07:55.851 --> 07:56.894
No one shouts.

08:00.230 --> 08:04.026
He doesn't shout because his players
know exactly what to do.

08:04.902 --> 08:07.446
Okay, all right. Nice to meet you.

08:55.619 --> 08:57.037
Tactical order.

08:58.288 --> 08:59.831
Athletic ability.

09:01.083 --> 09:02.334
Collective discipline.

09:07.547 --> 09:11.218
That's the identity he wants
for FC Barcelona.

09:11.301 --> 09:12.928
He knows you're tired,

09:13.011 --> 09:15.806
You have to be,
otherwise you're doing it wrong.

09:16.515 --> 09:19.518
You're here because you were chosen
for being the best.

09:21.728 --> 09:23.146
The best are still at...

09:23.230 --> 09:26.441
If you came here thinking
you'd actually play soccer, forget it.

09:26.525 --> 09:28.527
We didn't even touch a ball.

09:28.735 --> 09:31.697
Luckily, because he uses 20-pound balls.

09:31.780 --> 09:34.241
To strengthen the legs.

09:34.324 --> 09:36.576
That's all for today. You can go.

09:36.660 --> 09:38.787
We'll see you tomorrow at 7:00 a.m.

09:38.870 --> 09:41.123
here at the field, as usual.

09:41.248 --> 09:43.458
You train at 7:00 a.m. every day?

09:43.542 --> 09:45.043
Even on game days.

09:46.878 --> 09:49.923
By the way, Jorge, I was told

09:50.007 --> 09:52.968
it'd be better
if you didn't stay for practice.

09:54.720 --> 09:56.221
I don't see the problem.

09:56.471 --> 09:58.307
I was quiet the whole practice.

09:58.390 --> 10:01.393
Yes, it's just a request from the coach.

10:01.476 --> 10:02.811
Really?

10:02.894 --> 10:04.646
I've been with Diego for 10 years,

10:04.730 --> 10:06.565
- this has never happened to me.
- Yes.

10:06.648 --> 10:10.777
I understand Mr. Lattek
doesn't want to favor any players.

10:11.528 --> 10:13.238
Of course, don't worry.

10:13.322 --> 10:15.365
- I won't come back.
- Okay.

10:22.497 --> 10:23.498
What's up, Rengo?

10:24.458 --> 10:25.500
It's nothing.

10:25.584 --> 10:26.710
You look upset, why?

10:26.793 --> 10:28.503
They don't want me at practice.

10:28.587 --> 10:31.715
- He said that?
- No, relax, Diego, it's the coach.

10:31.798 --> 10:33.925
Oh, him? Hey, Udo!

10:34.009 --> 10:36.386
- This is on day one?
- Relax, Diego.

10:36.470 --> 10:38.221
Don't make a fuss about this.

10:38.305 --> 10:41.183
They've been kicking me
in the head from the get-go.

10:41.266 --> 10:43.518
Relax, Pelusa.

10:43.602 --> 10:46.646
It's not like I'm dying to see
guys doing push-ups.

10:46.730 --> 10:50.400
The important thing is that you had
your debut practice with Barcelona.

10:50.484 --> 10:53.653
I'm so proud. Give me a hug, man.

10:55.072 --> 10:56.782
I'm very happy.

10:56.865 --> 11:02.704
I'm sure Barcelona is heading to one
of the best periods in its history.

11:03.372 --> 11:07.042
<i>Towards winning the title</i>
<i>we've been fighting for a long time.</i>

11:07.125 --> 11:10.003
<i>We can boast that we have</i>
<i>the best player in the world.</i>

11:10.087 --> 11:11.922
<i>In a sold-out stadium,</i>

11:12.005 --> 11:15.342
<i>Diego Armando Maradona makes</i>
<i>his debut wearing blue and red.</i>

11:15.425 --> 11:20.097
<i>This afternoon is not only the start</i>
<i>of Maradona's destiny in Europe,</i>

11:20.180 --> 11:25.560
<i>but also Josep Lluís Nuñez's future</i>
<i>as head of FC Barcelona is at stake.</i>

11:26.812 --> 11:29.564
<i>A few moments before the game starts,</i>

11:29.648 --> 11:33.819
<i>and Diego Maradona greets</i>
<i>his compatriot Mario Alberto Kempes,</i>

11:33.902 --> 11:38.281
<i>Maradona's partner on the national team,</i>
<i>and and idol of Valencian fans.</i>

11:38.365 --> 11:41.618
<i>The game starts</i>
<i>with Diego Armando Maradona.</i>

11:41.701 --> 11:43.161
<i>It's the Argentinian's debut.</i>

11:43.245 --> 11:47.416
<i>Maradona is being marked by Kempes,</i>
<i>a duel between compatriots.</i>

11:47.499 --> 11:49.960
<i>Maradona keeps going, ball in the area.</i>

11:50.043 --> 11:53.130
<i>The goal is unguarded.</i>
<i>It's wide open for Maradona,</i>

11:53.213 --> 11:55.215
<i>it's a goal! Goal for Barcelona.</i>

11:55.298 --> 11:58.677
<i>It's Diego Armando Maradona's first goal!</i>

11:59.928 --> 12:02.722
<i>Watch out, Valencia attacks</i>
<i>with Tendillo. Goal!</i>

12:02.806 --> 12:05.559
<i>Goal for Valencia! Tendillo. It's a tie!</i>

12:05.642 --> 12:08.895
<i>Ball in the area, and it's Idigoras,</i>
<i>another goal!</i>

12:08.979 --> 12:12.899
<i>Valencia beats Barcelona 2-1</i>
<i>on Diego Armando Maradona's debut.</i>

12:12.983 --> 12:16.153
<i>Maradona is a great player,</i>
<i>there's no doubt about it.</i>

12:16.236 --> 12:19.614
<i>But soccer is a sport of 11 against 11.</i>

12:20.198 --> 12:24.870
<i>Come on. Jorge, will he be here all day?</i>
<i>He's even filming me taking a shit.</i>

12:24.953 --> 12:29.624
<i>I've been thinking of bringing Galíndez</i>
<i>over to help me with the ankle thing.</i>

12:29.708 --> 12:31.293
<i>This is Néstor.</i>

12:31.376 --> 12:33.879
<i>He takes me for rides,</i>
<i>he drives me around,</i>

12:33.962 --> 12:38.800
<i>-and he fucks lots of Galician girls.</i>
<i>-That's what they say.</i>

12:38.884 --> 12:42.888
<i>Osvaldito and I were</i>
<i>in little league together. Look at him.</i>

12:42.971 --> 12:44.639
<i>This is Morsa.</i>

12:44.723 --> 12:47.267
<i>My brother-in-law.</i>
<i>No one knows how he got here,</i>

12:47.350 --> 12:49.186
<i>or why he came, but...</i>

12:49.269 --> 12:51.062
<i>You can see that...</i>

12:51.354 --> 12:55.317
<i>My mom put him in a suitcase</i>
<i>to get him out of her way.</i>

12:55.525 --> 12:58.820
<i>Yeah, sure, suck on this. Oh, sorry!</i>

12:58.904 --> 13:00.655
<i>This is Rengo.</i>

13:00.906 --> 13:04.034
<i>This is a very fancy neighborhood</i>

13:04.493 --> 13:06.786
<i>with narrow streets. Very nice.</i>

13:06.870 --> 13:12.209
<i>I put a Barcelona badge in the pool,</i>
<i>to honor the team.</i>

13:12.292 --> 13:15.712
<i>I use this one when it's cloudy,</i>
<i>when the weather's bad.</i>

13:15.795 --> 13:17.839
<i>When the day is nice and sunny,</i>

13:17.923 --> 13:22.719
<i>I use this one, right?</i>
<i>But look at this one, look at this beauty.</i>

13:24.095 --> 13:25.931
<i>It's 200 horsepower. Listen.</i>

13:36.191 --> 13:41.696
<i>Some jealous people will say Maradona</i>
<i>wastes his money, and you know what?</i>

13:42.447 --> 13:44.950
<i>They're right, because I earn my money,</i>

13:45.033 --> 13:46.451
<i>I know how the world works.</i>

13:46.535 --> 13:48.537
<i>If you're blond with blue eyes,</i>

13:48.620 --> 13:50.997
<i>come from a good family,</i>
<i>you can do whatever.</i>

13:51.081 --> 13:54.042
<i>But if you're dark like us,</i>
<i>you'll be criticized.</i>

13:54.125 --> 13:56.586
<i>Right, guys? Let's tell it like it is.</i>

13:56.670 --> 13:58.797
<i>I thought this was only in Argentina,</i>

13:58.880 --> 14:02.259
<i>but then you come here,</i>
<i>and realize what's going on,</i>

14:02.342 --> 14:04.886
<i>because they start saying</i>
<i>Maradona isn't classy,</i>

14:04.970 --> 14:07.180
<i>the class Barcelona is used to.</i>

14:07.264 --> 14:09.933
<i>And that Maradona</i>
<i>hangs out with ugly people.</i>

14:10.016 --> 14:13.186
<i>Who the fuck do they think they are?</i>

14:13.270 --> 14:15.772
<i>They want us here, in Europe,</i>

14:15.855 --> 14:19.568
<i>for washing dishes and wiping their asses.</i>

14:19.651 --> 14:23.196
<i>Otherwise, they don't want us at all.</i>
<i>Why don't you go fuck yourselves?</i>

14:23.280 --> 14:25.282
<i>Stop breaking my balls, stop filming.</i>

14:25.365 --> 14:26.908
<i>Stop filming! Cut!</i>

14:32.872 --> 14:35.792
Let's give a warm welcome

14:35.875 --> 14:38.795
to Barcelona's amazing new player,

14:38.878 --> 14:41.214
Diego Armando Maradona!

14:48.430 --> 14:50.640
And now I am pleased to present

14:50.724 --> 14:52.559
another Argentine talent,

14:52.642 --> 14:54.477
with a voice to fall in love to...

14:54.561 --> 14:57.314
It's Lorena Gaumón!

15:04.779 --> 15:07.490
It's a pleasure to be here
with you tonight.

15:19.127 --> 15:21.838
<i>My love</i>

15:21.921 --> 15:26.426
<i>Don't worry, I won't bother you</i>

15:27.427 --> 15:32.098
<i>My luck was out, I know</i>

15:32.724 --> 15:38.313
<i>And I know there's a storm</i>
<i>Running through your mind</i>

15:38.396 --> 15:40.732
<i>My love</i>

15:41.024 --> 15:45.612
<i>Our encounter was just by chance</i>

15:46.112 --> 15:50.325
<i>Same time, same boulevard</i>

15:51.493 --> 15:57.082
<i>Don't be afraid, don't worry</i>
<i>I don't blame you for the past</i>

15:57.165 --> 16:01.795
<i>You see, life is like that</i>

16:02.212 --> 16:07.592
<i>You'll leave and I'll stay here</i>

16:07.676 --> 16:12.138
<i>It will rain</i>
<i>And I will no longer be yours</i>

16:12.806 --> 16:18.645
<i>I'll be the cat in the rain</i>

16:18.770 --> 16:22.565
<i>And I will meow for you</i>

16:31.825 --> 16:34.202
<i>My love</i>

16:34.786 --> 16:39.582
<i>I know, don't say anything</i>

16:39.666 --> 16:45.088
<i>If you see any tears, I'm sorry</i>

16:45.547 --> 16:51.052
<i>I know you didn't want to make</i>
<i>A wounded cat cry</i>

16:51.136 --> 16:53.596
<i>My love</i>

16:53.680 --> 16:58.560
<i>If we ever see each other</i>

16:59.185 --> 17:03.606
<i>Buy me a coffee and make love to me</i>

17:04.274 --> 17:06.526
<i>And if I never see you again</i>

17:06.609 --> 17:09.696
<i>I hope you're lucky</i>

17:09.821 --> 17:14.492
<i>You see, life is like that</i>

17:14.951 --> 17:19.622
<i>You'll leave and I'll stay here</i>

17:20.123 --> 17:24.961
<i>It will rain</i>
<i>And I will no longer be yours</i>

17:25.462 --> 17:31.259
<i>I'll be the cat in the rain</i>

17:31.509 --> 17:36.598
<i>And I will meow</i>

17:36.681 --> 17:40.351
<i>For you</i>

17:55.533 --> 18:00.205
<i>And I will meow for you</i>

18:10.131 --> 18:11.299
Yes, come in.

18:19.516 --> 18:20.767
Look who it is.

18:22.268 --> 18:23.603
My guest of honor.

18:24.771 --> 18:26.231
Diego Armando Maradona.

18:27.816 --> 18:30.109
- Nice to meet you, Diego.
- Pleasure.

18:30.193 --> 18:32.987
- Did you like the show?
- Yes, it was great.

18:33.780 --> 18:34.697
You know...

18:35.782 --> 18:37.325
We have a lot in common.

18:37.909 --> 18:38.743
Really?

18:39.786 --> 18:41.704
How do you know? We just met.

18:42.872 --> 18:44.123
We're Argentinians,

18:45.208 --> 18:47.126
we both came to conquer Europe.

18:47.293 --> 18:48.711
You like boleros,

18:49.712 --> 18:51.422
- and I like you.
- No, no.

18:52.173 --> 18:53.716
I didn't come to conquer.

18:54.717 --> 18:57.220
I just came to enjoy
what I do. That's all.

18:59.013 --> 18:59.931
I did.

19:06.646 --> 19:07.730
Want to go out?

19:10.525 --> 19:11.985
An ambiguous question.

19:13.319 --> 19:15.280
You mean go out someday?

19:16.531 --> 19:18.241
Or get out of here right now?

20:04.662 --> 20:05.872
Nice building.

20:06.372 --> 20:07.707
Must be beautiful inside.

20:07.790 --> 20:09.751
Don't even think about it.

20:09.834 --> 20:11.419
- Why not?
- You can't.

20:11.544 --> 20:14.672
- Not even for a cup of coffee?
- No coffee for you.

20:14.756 --> 20:17.425
Don't look at me like that.
You have practice

20:17.508 --> 20:19.177
and coffee will keep you up.

20:19.260 --> 20:20.845
You better go to sleep.

20:21.429 --> 20:24.098
You barely know me
and you're taking care of me.

20:24.182 --> 20:27.644
I'm not. I'm taking care of myself.

20:30.104 --> 20:32.065
- Thanks for the lift.
- You're welcome.

20:32.482 --> 20:33.733
- Okay, bye.
- Bye.

20:48.081 --> 20:49.248
You're terrible.

20:51.834 --> 20:53.544
You'll have to wait for more.

20:56.631 --> 20:58.466
