Not even for Diego Armando Maradona?

42:18.203 --> 42:20.247
For nobody, Jorgito.

42:20.330 --> 42:24.251
I can't wait for Diego to propose to me
so that I can shove my job.

42:26.044 --> 42:27.128
Only to women.

42:31.132 --> 42:33.468
You wouldn't give
anything up for me?

42:34.344 --> 42:36.846
What about you?
Would you stop playing for me?

42:37.639 --> 42:38.556
I wouldn't.

42:39.015 --> 42:40.100
See, darling?

42:40.517 --> 42:41.434
Me neither.

42:49.943 --> 42:51.403
Diego, your eyes look odd.

42:52.320 --> 42:54.739
It's your fault, you drive me crazy.

42:59.744 --> 43:01.413
Hey, what's that over there?

43:02.122 --> 43:03.873
- See?
- What?

43:03.957 --> 43:06.334
- That thing over there.
- Is it people?

43:07.127 --> 43:08.461
It's two people.

43:11.506 --> 43:13.133
- Yes, it's two people.
- Let's go.

43:13.216 --> 43:15.051
Come, Ladilla, hurry, man!

43:15.969 --> 43:18.930
They're drowning, let's go!

43:25.812 --> 43:26.646
Diego!

43:30.025 --> 43:32.610
Go get some towels. Diego!

43:34.446 --> 43:35.989
The towels, come on!

43:40.493 --> 43:42.078
- Diego!
- Come on, you got this.

43:42.370 --> 43:43.830
Be careful, Diego!

43:45.373 --> 43:47.667
Get them up there.

43:47.959 --> 43:50.295
- Over there.
- Osvaldo!

44:00.096 --> 44:03.808
Okay, are you all right?

44:03.892 --> 44:05.477
Are you okay?

44:06.311 --> 44:07.520
It's okay.

44:07.604 --> 44:09.230
Don't worry, we won't bite.

44:09.814 --> 44:12.025
They thought we were cannibals.

44:12.108 --> 44:13.943
Make her a chorizo sandwich.

44:14.027 --> 44:16.237
- I'm on it.
- Make her one.

44:16.988 --> 44:19.324
- Unbelievable.
- Okay.

44:19.449 --> 44:20.450
MARADONA'S
NEWS AGAIN

44:20.533 --> 44:21.368
CASTAWAY

44:21.451 --> 44:23.495
DIEGO AND HIS BLONDES TO THE RESCUE

44:24.537 --> 44:26.122
Motherfuckers.

44:26.623 --> 44:30.043
Instead of publishing Maradona
saved two people from drowning,

44:30.126 --> 44:34.005
they say I was on a yacht
with drugs, alcohol and naked chicks.

44:34.130 --> 44:35.423
Easy, Diego.

44:35.507 --> 44:38.468
I got the Germans, who are very grateful,

44:38.802 --> 44:41.638
to tell the story on the news.

44:41.721 --> 44:44.015
You were on a yacht
with friends, barbecue.

44:44.099 --> 44:46.101
Why don't we put Diego on the air?

44:46.810 --> 44:49.020
- The Germans will get emotional.
- Good idea.

44:49.687 --> 44:51.898
Is this bullshit I'm paying you for?

44:51.981 --> 44:56.820
Can't you see, once it's published,
people won't forget it so easily?

44:56.903 --> 44:59.072
At least they didn't
mention Lorena, Diego.

44:59.155 --> 45:01.991
I don't get what Nuñez gets
out of all of this.

45:02.075 --> 45:06.538
I talked to my journalist friends,
and Diego is right, this is all Nuñez.

45:06.621 --> 45:09.499
He wants the advertising deals
to fall through,

45:10.166 --> 45:12.168
so Diego depends on his salary.

45:12.252 --> 45:13.711
He wants us tied to him.

45:13.795 --> 45:16.339
I don't care what that motherfucker wants.

45:16.756 --> 45:18.258
I'll hit him where it hurts.

45:18.883 --> 45:22.137
When is the friendly tour?

45:26.683 --> 45:27.684
Friday the 15th.

45:31.020 --> 45:31.980
Diego.

45:32.689 --> 45:33.565
Diego!

45:35.191 --> 45:39.028
<i>Get one of those celebrity doctors,</i>
<i>the ones who like to perform,</i>

45:39.112 --> 45:42.532
so he can explain the after-effects
that Diego might have

45:42.615 --> 45:44.492
if he survives all of this.

45:44.826 --> 45:46.870
All right. I'll get on it.

45:46.953 --> 45:50.790
Do you know a Ferro Viera?
He became friends with Coppola in jail.

45:50.874 --> 45:54.335
Yes, he's been glued to Diego's ass
for a few years now.

45:54.419 --> 45:58.339
Guillermo's secretary.
Diego's personal assistant.

45:58.590 --> 46:01.009
- Yes.
- I'd publish something like this.

46:04.012 --> 46:06.473
Okay, go. Let me know when you get it.

46:07.223 --> 46:08.057
Go on.

46:10.185 --> 46:12.103
Come on, man, let me go.

46:12.187 --> 46:15.023
How much do you want?
My dad has lots of companies.

46:16.524 --> 46:19.903
- Hey, move over.
- Easy, old man.

46:20.945 --> 46:23.323
Man, I can't believe this.

46:23.656 --> 46:25.033
Guillote.

46:25.116 --> 46:27.160
Get the coke, let's do a few lines.

46:27.243 --> 46:29.287
Come on, you've got the best stuff.

46:30.288 --> 46:31.623
Quiet down.

46:31.915 --> 46:33.583
Lower your voice.

46:33.917 --> 46:37.962
Want to get your anal cavity checked
over a lousy joke?

46:39.088 --> 46:40.715
You're awesome, Guille.

46:40.840 --> 46:43.426
When I tell my folks,
they won't believe it.

46:43.968 --> 46:46.304
What did you do to end up here?

46:46.387 --> 46:48.473
Hide cocaine in a vase again, Guille?

46:48.556 --> 46:51.309
- Come on, man.
- Lying son of a bitch.

46:51.392 --> 46:53.478
Calm down, kids.

46:53.686 --> 46:57.899
- You've never seen a guy like me?
- Relax, Guillote.

46:57.982 --> 46:59.692
We're all friends here.

47:00.109 --> 47:01.277
Tell us.

47:01.569 --> 47:05.698
Is it true that you stopped for gas
while Diego was dying?

47:06.783 --> 47:07.742
Guillote.

47:08.326 --> 47:09.661
We really are friends.

47:09.911 --> 47:11.996
For you, Diego's better dead than alive.

47:12.080 --> 47:15.833
The fat man isn't bringing in money,
not even for his wife.

47:15.917 --> 47:18.962
- Hey, don't get mad.
- Son of a bitch.

47:19.921 --> 47:23.258
I can't believe my shitty luck.
Fucking assholes.

47:30.014 --> 47:32.267
Urruti, sing a capella.

47:32.767 --> 47:34.227
He started already.

47:44.153 --> 47:45.905
Eight whiskeys, just in case.

47:48.157 --> 47:51.202
Why haven't we taken the measures
to prevent this?

47:51.286 --> 47:54.205
We can say Maradona
had a personal problem.

47:54.289 --> 47:58.042
- A health problem. A relative died.
- No, Paco, don't be ridiculous.

47:58.126 --> 48:00.086
We can't go to Paris without Maradona.

48:00.753 --> 48:03.715
Who wants to watch a game
with these poor bastards?

48:05.133 --> 48:06.217
The car is here.

48:06.301 --> 48:08.136
Look, here he comes.

48:45.590 --> 48:47.550
Where the fuck is Maradona?

48:48.217 --> 48:50.094
- Maradona isn't coming.
- What?

48:50.178 --> 48:53.723
He learned about an unfair
situation for his teammates

48:53.806 --> 48:55.475
and won't accept it.

48:55.558 --> 48:57.810
- What are you saying?
- In order to travel,

48:58.686 --> 49:01.230
- Maradona has one condition.
- Condition?

49:01.314 --> 49:05.485
He gets a bonus for every game won,
but none of his teammates do.

49:05.568 --> 49:09.197
He wants everyone to get the same bonus
for a victory as he does.

49:09.280 --> 49:10.448
He's lost it.

49:10.990 --> 49:12.784
He can't make demands.

49:12.867 --> 49:15.411
- That can't be allowed.
- Then he's not coming.

49:15.495 --> 49:18.039
I don't know
if Maradona's decision is right,

49:18.122 --> 49:20.583
I came here to tell you
his requirements.

49:20.667 --> 49:24.545
You should if Barcelona
needs Maradona for these games or not.

49:24.629 --> 49:26.381
Have I treated him badly?

49:26.839 --> 49:29.133
Haven't I spent every penny on him?

49:31.636 --> 49:33.304
All right, tell him to come,

49:33.388 --> 49:35.765
we'll pay the whole team
the same bonus as him.

49:35.848 --> 49:37.975
There is one more small detail.

49:38.768 --> 49:41.854
- He wants everything in writing.
- Take care of this.

49:44.691 --> 49:47.568
It's all here. You don't have
to do anything, just sign.

49:57.120 --> 49:59.664
Diego, Diego!

50:00.707 --> 50:01.958
Long live Barcelona!

50:03.000 --> 50:04.168
Hurray!

50:18.766 --> 50:22.145
OH LA LA! PARIS AT NIGHT
THEY PLAYED HARD AND PARTIED HARDER

50:24.856 --> 50:27.525
<i>The photos that have</i>
<i>appeared in the newspapers</i>

50:27.608 --> 50:32.947
<i>were taken as part of a celebration</i>
<i>for the Barcelona's wins.</i>

50:33.030 --> 50:34.073
NON STOP PARTYING

50:34.157 --> 50:37.493
But they don't represent
the philosophy of our club,

50:37.577 --> 50:40.705
<i>so I'm going to have</i>
<i>a conversation with Maradona.</i>

50:40.788 --> 50:42.039
NUÑEZ - MARADONA
AT WAR?

50:47.587 --> 50:50.089
I can do what I want, when I want,

50:50.173 --> 50:52.884
as long as it doesn't affect
my performance...

50:52.967 --> 50:54.761
MARADONA AND BARCELONA
OUT PARTYING

50:54.844 --> 50:56.471
<i>...it's no one's business.</i>

50:57.930 --> 50:59.974
PARTY AFTER PARTY!
BARCELONA'S SEASON

51:00.057 --> 51:02.018
GIRLS AND ALCOHOL,
IT CAN'T GO ON.

51:04.645 --> 51:07.190
ARGENTINIAN STAR IS IN GOOD COMPANY

51:07.732 --> 51:10.485
I've already read the remarks
about his glassy eyes.

51:10.568 --> 51:11.944
WILL THERE BE A MEETING?

51:12.028 --> 51:13.654
I'll ask Diego to explain.

51:13.738 --> 51:18.284
<i>Glassy eyes? What are you saying, man?</i>
<i>That I drink alcohol?</i>

51:18.367 --> 51:20.828
That I take drugs?
Come on, don't lie to people.

51:20.912 --> 51:23.998
If he doesn't change his attitude,
he'll find another club.

51:24.081 --> 51:26.042
Why did Nuñez hire me?

51:26.125 --> 51:28.211
To play soccer or to persecute me?

51:28.294 --> 51:30.338
That'll be all. No more comments.

51:30.421 --> 51:34.258
Let's talk soccer, man.
Call me when you want to talk soccer.

51:34.342 --> 51:36.052
I'm done. Excuse me.

51:45.353 --> 51:48.856
<i>At Camp Nou,</i>
<i>it's Barcelona versus Celta de Vigo.</i>

51:48.940 --> 51:50.733
<i>The ball goes to Maradona,</i>

51:50.817 --> 51:53.945
<i>he makes an attempt,</i>
<i>but the defender makes a strong entrance.</i>

51:54.028 --> 51:57.198
<i>We see the pain</i>
<i>in the Argentine star's face.</i>

51:57.281 --> 52:00.701
<i>Coach Lattek calls</i>
<i>for a substitution immediately.</i>

52:01.285 --> 52:04.038
<i>Maradona is on the ground,</i>
<i>and he looks fed up.</i>

52:07.583 --> 52:09.752
What's with the long faces?

52:10.670 --> 52:12.296
Who knows? I'm not in pain.

52:13.381 --> 52:14.841
Are you pregnant?

52:15.508 --> 52:17.009
Be serious, Rengo, come on.

52:19.846 --> 52:21.514
How long do I have to live?

52:22.849 --> 52:25.893
Blood tests reveal
acute type B viral hepatitis.

52:28.479 --> 52:29.313
What?

52:31.023 --> 52:33.025
Hepatitis B's the mildest, right?

52:33.109 --> 52:36.153
It's the most dangerous one.
Difficult to cure.

52:36.654 --> 52:38.823
You'll have to get absolute rest.

52:38.906 --> 52:42.076
The nutritionists at the club
will outline a diet,

52:42.159 --> 52:46.205
and your muscles might suffer some kind
of atrophy due to lack of exercise.

52:46.873 --> 52:50.835
So, we'll be looking at the need
for rehabilitation, okay?

52:51.586 --> 52:53.212
- Okay.
- Thanks, Doc.

52:56.799 --> 53:01.846
CONFIRMED: IT'S HEPATITIS!
DIEGO MARADONA CANNOT PLAY

53:17.528 --> 53:18.946
LATTEK OUT, MENOTTI IN

53:20.823 --> 53:22.158
Happy?

53:22.241 --> 53:23.492
I am now.

53:23.659 --> 53:25.119
Flaco is the best.

53:26.162 --> 53:29.373
Lattek, you stupid asshole.

53:30.833 --> 53:33.085
He can go back to Germany
and eat sausages.

53:40.259 --> 53:41.385
Who's that?

53:44.013 --> 53:45.097
Bilardo?

53:54.732 --> 53:56.943
Easy, Carlos, you'll hurt yourself.

54:04.450 --> 54:06.035
It's very hot.

54:06.118 --> 54:07.995
It was hard to find you, Diego.

54:09.705 --> 54:13.209
You came all this way to meet me?

54:13.668 --> 54:17.088
- Did you like me?
- Yes. Very much.

54:17.171 --> 54:19.382
But I was sure I would.

54:19.465 --> 54:21.467
I didn't just come to meet you.

54:22.051 --> 54:24.720
To me, it's Maradona and 10 others.

54:24.804 --> 54:27.723
The national team, I mean.
Maradona and 10 others.

54:28.140 --> 54:29.141
What do you say?

54:31.060 --> 54:32.937
Carlos, I won't lie.

54:33.604 --> 54:36.190
I don't know if I'll get back
to the same level.

54:36.273 --> 54:37.608
You won't.

54:38.067 --> 54:39.402
You'll be even better.

54:39.860 --> 54:40.945
And I'll help you.

54:41.487 --> 54:44.657
I know your soccer taste is Menotti.

54:45.032 --> 54:46.993
We're different.

54:47.076 --> 54:50.579
We work differently,
but we agree on something.

54:50.663 --> 54:53.874
We all want to win,
but we have to make a pact.

54:53.958 --> 54:55.710
From my side, total freedom.

54:56.168 --> 54:58.629
You're friends with whoever, I don't care.

54:59.505 --> 55:02.633
You train, I'll help, you do you. But...

55:03.175 --> 55:05.261
You have to be loyal to me.

55:05.928 --> 55:08.931
Why? The press wants Menotti,
they don't want me.

55:09.015 --> 55:12.184
- They'll destroy us.
- Exactly, so, when it's needed,

55:12.351 --> 55:15.771
I need the best player in the world
to defend me.

55:16.313 --> 55:19.984
But I didn't just come to meet you,
I brought you something.

55:22.153 --> 55:23.279
I brought you this.

55:27.908 --> 55:29.410
You're my captain.

55:43.841 --> 55:45.051
What do you say?

55:54.310 --> 55:56.145
Yes, there you go.

55:58.814 --> 55:59.940
So?

56:00.649 --> 56:01.776
How does it feel?

56:03.736 --> 56:06.989
I feel like I'm wearing Superman's cape.

56:07.740 --> 56:09.909
Yes, you are Superman.

56:10.576 --> 56:14.622
Listen, let's take a walk,
I'll tell you about the project.

56:14.955 --> 56:17.750
It's different.
At first, you won't understand,

56:17.833 --> 56:19.627
but it will become clear to you.

56:19.710 --> 56:22.254
Come on, let's walk for a while.

56:23.881 --> 56:25.925
- What about Passarella?
- He's good.

56:26.008 --> 56:30.721
Passarella is a great player,
but he's the former coach's captain.

56:30.805 --> 56:32.598
You are my captain.

56:39.230 --> 56:42.483
Hepatitis left Diego Maradona
inactive for three months.

56:42.566 --> 56:45.820
The Catalan press harassed him,
spreading false rumors.

56:46.612 --> 56:50.324
They claimed his eyes were yellowish
due to drug consumption,

56:50.407 --> 56:52.618
that he had a venereal disease,

56:52.701 --> 56:56.914
that he suffered from gonorrhea
and would never play soccer again.

56:57.373 --> 57:00.417
Coaches Carlos Bilardo
and his predecessor, Cesar Menotti,

57:00.501 --> 57:03.546
started a battle of styles
that continues to this day.

57:03.796 --> 57:06.841
Menotti's supporters favor
an offensive and ostentatious game

57:06.924 --> 57:12.471
while Bilardo's, strategy and sacrifice.
The end (victory) justifies the means.

57:13.430 --> 57:15.141
<i>Diego, at 21 years of age,</i>

57:15.266 --> 57:18.561
<i>how does it feel to be constantly</i>
<i>surrounded by the public,</i>

57:18.644 --> 57:20.896
by fans, by police protection,

57:21.021 --> 57:23.315
by so many people who want to touch you,

57:23.399 --> 57:24.942
hug you, shake your hand?

57:26.652 --> 57:31.782
First of all,
I don't need police protection

57:31.866 --> 57:34.201
to walk down the street, I don't need...

57:34.994 --> 57:40.958
Anyone. People love me,
and I love people too.

58:01.437 --> 58:05.232
In 1983, when I took charge
of the national team,

58:05.858 --> 58:09.653
I went to Barcelona to see Maradona,
and told him he'd be captain.

58:09.737 --> 58:11.614
And when I got here, I announced,

58:11.697 --> 58:14.116
"The new headliner and captain
is Maradona."

58:14.200 --> 58:18.370
I had to leave the country for 10 days.
They wanted to kill me.

58:18.913 --> 58:21.749
I said he would be
one of the best players,

58:22.374 --> 58:24.835
and people told me all kinds of things.

58:24.960 --> 58:27.796
Remember, the captain
at that time was Passarella.

58:27.880 --> 58:29.048
I recognize that.

58:29.131 --> 58:31.717
Passarella, but Maradona
would be a good player.

59:25.646 --> 59:29.275
<i>Today we're celebrating</i>
<i>Diego's pre-birthday,</i>

59:29.358 --> 59:31.777
<i>so it's Maradona Christmas Eve.</i>

59:31.860 --> 59:35.781
<i>We'll wait until 12:00,</i>
<i>then we'll count up</i>

59:35.864 --> 59:38.826
from one to 10, to 12:00,

59:38.909 --> 59:42.871
to celebrate Diego's birthday,
which is our Maradonian Christmas.
